snippet.title: "Mario Left The Cheese Out" fangame playthrough
snippet.description:
Click the Closed Captions button for crummy commentary.
A playthrough of 'Mario Left The Cheese Out', a 2003 fangame by 4 Eyes.
You can download the game for yourself here: http://www.mfgg.net/index.php?act=resdb&param=02&c=2&id=281

Mario destroys alien wildlife, the MFGG community and more in his quest to get the secret cheese. A quirky game that made splashes with its visual effects and oddball humour.
